Contact me if you wish your asset to be removed from my website.

generate_rss.js
    this script generates rss.xml from blogs.json

data.json
    manually added stuff, like button paths and images, contacts, songs, settings, achievements, and other stuff that I will add later on.
    use case for this is to easily get data and generate html for it.

stats.json
    generated from update_stats.js appends daily stats from nekoweb, also adds most recent github commit message with all other data (lines changed etc..).

blogs are written to .md file and then generated to .html file with proper markdown and css styling with 11ty


